                        <div><p class="text-[10px] font-black text-indigo-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Topic: Shopping</p><p class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 leading-tight">How often do you go shopping?</p></div>
                    </div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> warm up 
Do you love shopping ?.
-> yes, i am shopping lover
when/where/with who
-> I usually shop at the weekend in the local shop nearby. I can shop alone however, i prefer to shop with friends.
Why do go shopping ?.
-> 1. sở thích -> giúp thư giãn VD: this is my hobby -> I often buys goods/products/things for my daily life.
Do you think go shopping in person friends is a great way to improve the relationship ?.  
-> 2. cách tốt -> dành thời gian nói chuyện với bạn bè. VD: i also think it is a great way to spend time with friends.
V-ed: người/ V-ing vật (I am bored/ the movie is boring).
