                        <div><p class="text-[10px] font-black text-indigo-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Topic: Shopping</p><p class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 leading-tight">Do you prefer large malls or small local shops? Why?</p></div>
                    </div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> Do you prefer large malls or small local shops? Why?
