1. Buying at the large malls will give me more options to choose from the shelve, which varies from sizes, types, materials, brands, etcetera (e séc tờ rờ)... (đa dạng về).    
2. The products always have price tags on itself so i do not need to bargain or ask for the price.
3. The supermarket also offer air-condition. It is comfortable.</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Respond to Questions (ID: P3-2.1)</h3><p><div class="glass-card p-6 flex items-center gap-6 group hover:translate-x-1 transition-all">
