-> The local people are very friend. I always ask for directions, Tourism attraction from them. They treat the tourist well and welcome = embrace with a smile on their face.
Tell me about a memories you have with people there ?.
-> mất chìa -> (cảm xúc) cảm thấy sợ -> có người giúp -> cảm xúc cuối -> bài học rút ra.
-> I used to get lost in the middle of nowhere. I was afraid at first but then i found some local people on the street. Luckily, they are willing to give me directions. From this experience, i felt very grateful and love Da Nang people. 
